        <mxCell id="DtVYKYvhivc_cz4grxBP-1" value="I want to be able to do interleaved data, and series data. But I dont want to force the user to know about it. I need a separate block or node type to manage these" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
